Flash Briefing Skill

des: The Hellgate Elementary School Menu skill for Amazon Alexa allows you to add the daily Breakfast and Lunch menu from Hellgate Elementary School in Missoula, MT to your flash briefing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
